t 1816 || 15 October 1816 || {{age in years and days|1816|8|16|1816|10|15}} || Wedel I\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Herman_Wedel-Jarlsberg_av_N\u00f8rregaard.jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Herman Wedel Jarlsberg]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 October 1816 || 15 October 1818 || {{age in years and days|1816|10|15|1818|10|15}} || Wedel I\n|-\n|}\n\n== Ministry of Finance, Trade and Customs (1818-1846) ==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=col class=unsortable | Photo\n! scope=col | Name\n! scope=col | Party\n! scope=col | Took office\n! scope=col | Left office\n! scope=col | Tenure\n! scope=col | Cabinet\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Jonas_Collett.png|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Jonas Collett]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 October 1818 || 30 November 1818|| {{age in years and days|1818|10|15|1818|11|30}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Herman_Wedel-Jarlsberg_av_N\u00f8rregaard.jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Herman Wedel Jarlsberg]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 30 November 1818 || 1 January 1822|| {{age in years and days|1818|11|30|1822|1|1}} || Wedel I\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Jonas_Collett.png|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Jonas Collett]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 1 January 1822|| 17 December 1836 || {{age in years and days|1822|1|1|1836|12|17}} || Wedel I-II\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:J._H._Vogt.png|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[J\u00f8rgen Herman Vogt]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] ||17 December 1836|| 15 May 1846 || {{age in years and days|1836|12|17|1846|5|15}} || Wedel II <br> L\u00f8venskiold/Vogt\n|-\n|}\n\n== Ministry of Finance and Customs (1846-1999) ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! Name !! From !! To\n\n|-\n|[[J\u00f8rgen Herman Vogt]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1846\n\n|-\