or Berge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1923\n|align=\"center\"|1924\n\n|-\n|[[Arnold Holmboe]]\n|align=\"center\"|1924\n|align=\"center\"|1926\n\n|-\n|[[Fredrik Ludvig Konow]]\n|align=\"center\"|1926\n|align=\"center\"|1928\n\n|-\n|[[Christopher Hornsrud]]\n|align=\"center\"|1928\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Per Berg Lund]]\n|align=\"center\"|1928\n|align=\"center\"|1931\n\n|-\n|[[Peder Ludvik Kolstad]]\n|align=\"center\"|1931\n|align=\"center\"|1932\n\n|-\n|[[Jon Sundby]] (acting)\n|align=\"center\"|1932\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Jon Sundby]]\n|align=\"center\"|1932\n|align=\"center\"|1933\n\n|-\n|[[Per Berg Lund]]\n|align=\"center\"|1933\n|align=\"center\"|1934\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Jahn]]\n|align=\"center\"|1934\n|align=\"center\"|1935\n\n|-\n|[[Adolf Indreb\u00f8]]\n|align=\"center\"|1935\n|align=\"center\"|1936\n\n|-\n|[[Kornelius Olai Person Bergsvik]]\n|align=\"center\"|1936\n|align=\"center\"|1939\n\n|-\n|[[Oscar Fredrik Torp]]\n|align=\"center\"|1939\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Jahn]] (Administrative Council in Oslo)\n|align=\"center\"|1940\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Oscar Fredrik Torp]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1941\n\n|-\n|[[Paul Ernst Wilhelm Hartmann]]\n|align=\"center\"|1941\n|align=\"center\"|1942\n\n|-\n|[[Oscar Fredrik Torp]]\n|align=\"center\"|1942\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Paul Ernst Wilhelm Hartmann]]\n|align=\"center\"|1942\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Egil Kaare Sundt]] (chief officer in Oslo)\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Paul Ernst Wilhelm Hartmann]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Jahn]]\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Erik Brofoss]]\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n|align=\"center\"|1947\n\n|-\n|[[Olav Meisdalshagen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1947\n|align=\"center\"|1951\n\n|-\n|[[Trygve Martin Bratteli]]\n|align=\"center\"|1951\n|align=\"center\"|1955\n\n|-\n|[[Mons Lid]]\n|align=\"center\"|1955\n|align=\"center\"|1956\n\n|-\n|[[Trygve Martin Bratt