[[Norwegian Ministry of Finance]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{NorwegianFinancialMinisters}}\n{{Ministers of Norway}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of government ministers of Norway|Finance]]\n[[Category:1814 establishments in Norway]]\n", "text_old": "The '''Minister of Finance''' is a [[Cabinet of Norway|councilor of state]] and chief of the [[Ministry of Finance (Norway)|Ministry of Finance]]. The position is since January 2020 held by [[Jan Tore Sanner]] of the [[Conservative Party (Norway)|Conservative Party]] who is a member of the [[Solberg's Cabinet]].\n\n{| border=1 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 align=right\n|-\n|colspan=2 align=center | '''Norwegian Ministers of Finance after 1945'''\n|-\n|colspan=2 align=center | <timeline>\n# All measures all in pixels\nImageSize  = width:200 height:670\nPlotArea   = width: 26 height:530 left:50 bottom:110 # alignment is wrong when plotarea width (25) equals bar width (25)\n                                                    # will be fixed in next EasyTimeline update\nAlignBars  = early\n\nDateFormat = yyyy\nPeriod     = from:1945 till:2021\nTimeAxis   = orientation:vertical\nScaleMajor = unit:year increment:4 start:1945\n\n# there is no automatic collision detection,\n# so shift texts up or down manually to avoid overlap\n\nDefine $dx = 25 # shift text to right side of bar\n\nLegend     = columns:1 left:20 top:60 columnwidth:300\n\nColors =\n id:AP value:red legend:Ap\n id:H value:blue legend:H\n id:KRF value:yellow legend:KrF\n id:SP value:green legend:SP\n id:V value:pink legend:V\n id:SV value:orange legend:SV\n id:FrP value:darkblue legend:FrP\n\nPlotData=\n  bar:Leaders width:25 mark:(line,white) align:left fontsize:S\n  from:1945  till:1947 shift:($dx,-2)   color:AP text:[[Erik Brofoss|Brofoss]]\n  from:1947  till:1951 shift:($dx,-2)   color:AP text:[[Olav Meisdalshagen|Meisdalshagen]]\n  from:1951  till:1955 shift:($dx,-2)   color:AP text:[[Trygve Martin Bratteli|Bratteli]]\n  from:1955  till:1956 shift:($dx,-2)   co