ger Kildal]]\n|align=\"center\"|1903\n|align=\"center\"|1904\n\n|-\n|[[Peter Christian Hersleb Kjerschow Michelsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1904\n|align=\"center\"|1905\n\n|-\n|[[Aanon Gunnar Knudsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1905\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Peter Christian Hersleb Kjerschow Michelsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1905\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Edvard Hagerup Bull]]\n|align=\"center\"|1905\n|align=\"center\"|1906\n\n|-\n|[[Abraham Theodor Berge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1906\n|align=\"center\"|1907\n\n|-\n|[[Johan Magnus Halvorsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1907\n|align=\"center\"|1908\n\n|-\n|[[Aanon Gunnar Knudsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1908\n|align=\"center\"|1910\n\n|-\n|[[Abraham Theodor Berge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1910\n|align=\"center\"|1912\n\n|-\n|[[Fredrik Ludvig Konow]]\n|align=\"center\"|1912\n|align=\"center\"|1913\n\n|-\n|[[Anton Thorkildsen Omholt]]\n|align=\"center\"|1913\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Otto Albert Blehr]] (acting)\n|align=\"center\"|1915\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Anton Thorkildsen Omholt]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1919\n\n|-\n|[[Aanon Gunnar Knudsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1919\n|align=\"center\"|1920\n\n|-\n|[[Edvard Hagerup Bull]]\n|align=\"center\"|1920\n|align=\"center\"|1921\n\n|-\n|[[Otto Albert Blehr]]\n|align=\"center\"|1921\n|align=\"center\"|1923\n\n|-\n|[[Abraham Theodor Berge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1923\n|align=\"center\"|1924\n\n|-\n|[[Arnold Holmboe]]\n|align=\"center\"|1924\n|align=\"center\"|1926\n\n|-\n|[[Fredrik Ludvig Konow]]\n|align=\"center\"|1926\n|align=\"center\"|1928\n\n|-\n|[[Christopher Hornsrud]]\n|align=\"center\"|1928\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Per Berg Lund]]\n|align=\"center\"|1928\n|align=\"center\"|1931\n\n|-\n|[[Peder Ludvik Kolstad]]\n|align=\"center\"|1931\n|align=\"center\"|1932\n\n|-\n|[[Jon Sundby]] (acting)\n|align=\"center\"|1932\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Jon Sundby]]\n|align=\"center\"|1932\n|align=\"center\"|1933\n\n|-\n|[[Per Berg Lund]]\n|align=\"center\"|1933\n|align=\"center\"|1934\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Jahn]]\n|align=\"center\"|1934\n|align=\"center\"|1935\n\n|-\n|[[Adolf Indreb\u00f8]]\n|align=\"center\"|1935\n|align=\"center\"|1936\n\n|-\n|[[Kornelius Olai Person Bergsvik]]\n|align=\"center\"|1936\n|align=\"center\"|1939\n\n|-\n|[[Oscar Fredrik Torp]]\n|align=\"center\"|1939\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Jahn]] (Administrative Council in Oslo)\n|align=\"center\"|1940\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Oscar Fredrik Torp]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1941\n\n|-\n|[[Paul Ernst Wilhelm Hartmann]]\n|align=\"center\"|1941\n|align=\"center\"|1942\n\n|-\n|[[Oscar Fredrik Torp]]\n|align=\"center\"|1942\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Paul Ernst Wilhelm Hartmann]]\n|align=\"center\"|1942\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Egil Kaare Sundt]] (chief officer in Oslo)\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Paul Ernst Wilhelm Hartmann]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Jahn]]\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Erik Brofoss]]\n|align=\"center\"|1945\n|align=\"center\"|1947\n\n|-\n|[[Olav Meisdalshagen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1947\n|align=\"center\"|1951\n\n|-\n|[[Trygve Martin Bratteli]]\n|align=\"center\"|1951\n|align=\"center\"|1955\n\n|-\n|[[Mons Lid]]\n|align=\"center\"|1955\n|align=\"center\"|1956\n\n|-\n|[[Trygve Martin Bratteli]]\n|align=\"center\"|1956\n|align=\"center\"|1960\n\n|-\n|[[Petter Jacob Bjerve]]\n|align=\"center\"|1960\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Trygve Martin Bratteli]] (acting)\n|align=\"center\"|1962\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Petter Jacob Bjerve]]\n|align=\"center\"|-\n|align=\"center\"|1963\n\n|-\n|[[Andreas Zeier Cappelen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1963\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Dagfinn V\u00e5rvik]]\n|align=\"center\"|1963\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Andreas Zeier Cappelen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1963\n|align=\"center\"|1965\n\n|-\n|[[Ole Myrvoll]]\n|align=\"center\"|1965\n|align=\"center\"|1971\n\n|-\n|[[Ragnar Christiansen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1971\n|align=\"center\"|1972\n\n|-\n|[[Jon Ola Norbom]]\n|align=\"center\"|1972\n|align=\"center\"|1973\n\n|-\n|[[Per Andreas Kleppe]]\n|align=\"center\"|1973\n|align=\"center\"|1976\n\n|-\n|[[Per Andreas Kleppe]]\n|align=\"center\"|1976\n|align=\"center\"|1979\n\n|-\n|[[Ulf Sand]]\n|align=\"center\"|1979\n|align=\"center\"|1981\n\n|-\n|[[Ulf Sand]]\n|align=\"center\"|1981\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Rolf Presthus]]\n|align=\"center\"|1981\n|align=\"center\"|1986\n\n|-\n|[[Arne Skauge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1986\n|align=\"center\"|-\n\n|-\n|[[Gunnar Berge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1986\n|align=\"center\"|1989\n\n|-\n|[[Arne Skauge]]\n|align=\"center\"|1989\n|align=\"center\"|1990\n\n|-\n|[[Sigbj\u00f8rn Johnsen]]\n|align=\"center\"|1990\n|align=\"center\"|1996\n\n|-\n|[[Jens Stoltenberg]]\n|align=\"center\"|1996\n|align=\"center\"|1997\n\n|-\n|[[Gudmund Restad]]\n|align=\"center\"|1997\n|align=\"center\"|2000\n\n|}\n\n== Ministry of Finance (2000-) ==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=col class=unsortable | Photo\n! scope=col | Name\n! scope=col | Party\n! scope=col | Took office\n! scope=col | Left office\n! scope=col | Tenure\n! scope=col | Cabinet\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Karl Eirik Schj\u00f8tt-Pedersen.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Karl Eirik Schj\u00f8tt-Pedersen]]\n| style=\"background:#FFB6B6\" | [[Labour Party (Norway)|Labour]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2000|03|17}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2001|10|19}} || {{ayd|2000|03|17|2001|10|19}} || [[First cabinet Stoltenberg|Stoltenberg I]] \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Per-Kristian Foss 20090913-1.JPG|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Per-Kristian Foss]]\n| style=\"background:#AACCFF\" | [[Conservative Party (Norway)|Conservative]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2001|10|19}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2005|10|17}} || {{ayd|2001|10|19|2005|10|17}} || [[Second cabinet Bondevik|Bondevik II]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Norges finansminister Kristin Halvorsen vid Nordiska Radets session i Helsingfors 2008-10-28 (1).jpg|100